["TEXT","e30",92,565,0,"Notes:","st4"]
["TEXT","e31",92,605,0,"- Non-synchronous buck topology: U1 switch node drives L1, D1 clamps SW to GND.","st8"]
["TEXT","e32",92,640,0,"- Choose U1, L1, D1, CIN/COUT ratings by VIN range, load current, ripple and switching frequency.","st8"]
["TEXT","e33",92,675,0,"- Add layout-critical loop: VIN -> U1 -> D1 -> GND -> CIN close and short.","st8"]
